{"tid":23624,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚飲大左 同左最好朋友上床","createTime":"2016-12-05T05:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T09:25:17.000Z","uid":11354,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca384f79667a4921302781551dd0bda42593793","tid":23624,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日女朋友去左日本旅行 <br />\n所以屋企得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住尋晚，我沖完涼 <br />\n發覺電話有十幾個misscall <br />\n原來我朋友岩岩比男友飛左 <br />\n喊哂口咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後傾左成個鐘電話 <br />\n佢忽然話：不如出來陪我飲酒？ <br />\n但係個陣已經成十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我見屋企無咩人 <br />\n又懶出去 <br />\n就話：不如你上來啦 我屋企又齊酒 <br />\n有私人空間又慳錢 <br />\n於是佢就上左來... <br />\n我地vodka,rum,啤酒,blue curacao, tequila <br />\n咩都溝下來飲 <br />\n結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然 <br />\n佢對眼水汪汪咁問我： <br />\n你可唔可以 錫我一淡？ <br />\n可能真係能成為密友大概總帶著愛 <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去 <br />\n結果我地越咀越激 <br />\n互相纏住大家條頸 <br />\n舌頭交纏住咁行左入我房 <br />\n一攤上床 <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙 <br />\n詳細就唔多講 <br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n大家都出左三次先攬住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家覺得好對唔住女朋友 <br />\n同埋覺得同佢既友誼變左質 <br />\n巴絲你地話點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0447985749aeeb82526fb8152607f7bf5fd9f8d0","tid":23624,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"11月26 你開過啦， 月經？"},{"pid":"b5c9d5e097ab5eff75ed1a8a6091982af3e9c4c4","tid":23624,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:09:51.000Z","msg":"好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c0d09feeaa6022579b863cf58fdd59ddf5e09d","tid":23624,"uid":6317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"大家都出左3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3344ba6806b52bad4ceb8aa5d1b4396a35c0dac","tid":23624,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11月26 你開過啦， 月經？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋晚既事 好苦惱"},{"pid":"344a4b3e3b9208ba1656a409cd32e03f1d52452b","tid":23624,"uid":20959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>11月26 你開過啦， 月經？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋晚既事 好苦惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第三次回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就變日經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61384109d14d8a2745e5e44345ebfef361a4a47","tid":23624,"uid":46831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"好耐無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71e95354ebd395dfa8431f174a27c404f167c81","tid":23624,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"176a2247e7f34e4993b49946d6abe6fa46e526e8","tid":23624,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"Alexbb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe0397ea495a20eada2304bcd886cf1fe7e02f5","tid":23624,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"醒呀！唔好訓呀！"},{"pid":"1fecadcc1734bb45ede10e4e8b5eba8bdb8431b3","tid":23624,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醒呀！唔好訓呀！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c911c5e233ec05814477c674d645b776e7e35ed3","tid":23624,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"鐘意左同學parent<br />\n<br />\n勁後生 望落30歲尾倒 眼大大 個body好撚正 成日著d低胸 貼身褲 個形現晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自從有次去同學屋企打機就一見鐘情了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後成日借頭借路約去同學屋企打機做功課之類佢勁熱情 成日望住我地笑笑口 <br />\n<br />\n點知有日係同學度屋企做功課做得耐 去下廁所 竟然發現佢係入面痾尿冇鎖門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢都好唔知點 佢擰轉頭望我笑一笑就山返度門 我就傻左咁企起度....."},{"pid":"632cc757e323dd2df178a1c1a60ad90016c505c5","tid":23624,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/132610_447b7d4e877e7f18e09c4df295ac8104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F132610_447b7d4e877e7f18e09c4df295ac8104.jpg&h=701d5a60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a22d56d197d85f4b18c5510fa0e99edcabcf0a27","tid":23624,"uid":25461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩"},{"pid":"d873cbdd374ff5ff23138076fc99b7f4ad03e77f","tid":23624,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"三次好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d996d375b788565f4c2672eb1d40327a3bbf574","tid":23624,"uid":10702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三次好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n渣架"},{"pid":"7355a5928cf4f09385003369b5740c79549f6093","tid":23624,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"頂 我估背影呀今次"},{"pid":"352e880deb1563643debbc371229ed7d309b92ac","tid":23624,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{